#下面开始技术总结
Next, technical summary

0:04:39.140,0:04:44.040
#第一，鱼不可选择太大否则不嫩，一般两斤半以内最合适
First, the fish should not be too large, or it may not be tender enough. Generally a fish under 1250 grams would be fine.

0:04:44.040,0:04:49.580
