Second, the marinated fish must be mixed with oil before frying, or it will definitely stick together

0:04:49.580,0:04:55.040
#第三，此菜可以略咸一些这样更加入味，正所谓咸鱼淡肉
Third, it's OK to make this dish a little saltier for better flavor penetration effect. As a saying goes, "salty fish and bland meat taste better" #请检查

